    <description>Ada TUI for managing rclone cloud mount configurations with rate limiting.

Cloud Sync Tuner provides an interactive terminal interface for configuring rclone
cloud mounts with optimal rate limiting settings. It generates service configurations
with appropriate VFS cache modes to prevent API rate limiting from cloud providers
like Dropbox.

Note: FUSE mounts are not available on Windows. This package provides remote
operations only (copy, sync, ls, etc.).</description>
    <summary>Configure rclone cloud mounts with rate limiting (CLI mode on Windows)</summary>
